00:00:31.370 --> 00:00:32.703 align:middle line:90%
Debra, welcome to Beyond Belief.

00:00:32.703 --> 00:00:34.745 align:middle line:84%
>>DEBRA MARTIN: Oh, thank
you for having me here.

00:00:34.745 --> 00:00:35.590 align:middle line:90%
