You do, too.

00:00:38.050 --> 00:00:39.860 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: What are you doing?

00:00:39.860 --> 00:00:43.010 align:middle line:84%
>>MARTIN: I'm just living
life and trying to bring joy

00:00:43.010 --> 00:00:44.360 align:middle line:90%
